quran[6]{c,v,t,f}:
  15,34,"(Allah) jwatite: “Basi kopokani mwalakwemo, mwanti chisimu mmwe (sano) n’di ŵakuŵinjidwa.”"
  15,35,"“Soni chisimu pachanya penu pana malweso mpaka Lisiku Lyamalipilo.”"
  15,36,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Ambuje ŵangu! Mumbanitu lipesa (lyakuti ngawa) mpaka lisiku lyatachiukulidwa (m’malembe achiiumbe wosope).”"
  16,13,"Ni iliyose yan’guumbiile petaka (kutandila mitapo jambiya, yakumelamela kwisa soni inyama), yakulekangana mitundu jakwe (ni kaoneche kakwe), chisimu mu yalakweyo mwana chilosyo kwa ŵandu ŵakumbuchila."
  16,14,"Soni Jwalakwe ni Ajula jwaajijepepesye mbwani, kuti n’dyeje kuumila mwalakwemo nyama ja matumbi (somba), soni kuti mkoposyeje mwalakwemo ipeto yankasawalaga. Ni nkasaionaga soni yombo ili nkupapula matumbela mwalakwemo, kuti nsosejesoseje umbone Wakwe (wa Allah pakujigala misigo jenu jamalonda mu yombomo), ni kuti soni jenumanja m’be ŵakutogolela."
  16,15,"Ni aŵisile petaka yakunyichisya (matumbi gausito) kuti litakwika mulin’gwedanyichile ŵanganyammwe (litakalyo), ni (aŵisile) sulo kwisa soni matala kuti jenumanja n’dijongolele (mwachimisyene kwakuja)."